Half-man, half-goat, all attitude. The bariaur (BAR-ee-are) are rough-and-tumble warriors of a nomadic race, a straightforward people with a zest for life. They're native to Ysgard, but can also be found wandering the Outlands, Arborea, and the Beastlands. 

      Sources:&nbsp;
    
            
                    Planewalker&#039;s Handbook        
              
                    Manual of the Planes (D&amp;D 3.0)        
              
